originalText.text: This is the HSS hospital parking.  Do not park here!  It’s a complete rip-off!  I had to wait over 20 minutes to get into the garage  and another 15 minutes to get my car!  Do yourself a huge favor and use Spot Hero!  There are plenty of great nearby garages!

originalText.text:
This parking garage is terrible. I was having surgery at Hospital for Special Surgery. The parking attendant visually inspected my car and there wasn’t any damage when I first arrived. After surgery my wife pulled the car to front of the hospital. Her only concern at that point was making sure her and the hospital staff safely assisted me into my vehicle. When we arrived at home we realized the car was hit on the bumper and the fender and touch up paint was applied all of my new car. The manger and all his staff are aware of the accident and tried to cover it up and they continue to lie about hitting the car. Everyone is rude from the parking attendants to the corporate employees. DO NOT PARK THERE!!!!!!
I spoke to staff at Hospital for Special Surgery after the accident and I was very surprised that the staff does not park there because they too experienced damages to their personal Vehicles.
